Subject: [Rcpp-devel] Repeatedly evaluating external C++ function in
	the	same environment
In-Reply-To: <CAMoQLLd7H7SVUh1h-iBWigSH1U3F3NDPHMtZ=tSEPmx8w5Ta4g@mail.gmail.com>
References: <CAMoQLLd7H7SVUh1h-iBWigSH1U3F3NDPHMtZ=tSEPmx8w5Ta4g@mail.gmail.com>
