You probably have 

    Depends: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo

or

    Imports: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo

when you only need

    Imports: Rcpp
    LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo

See eg the RcppMLPACK package as a recent example, and edit your DESCRIPTION
accordingly. 

