#' @exportClass WKNND
#' @export WKNND
WKNND <- setRcppClass("WKNND")

(The full code is here 
https://github.com/jefferis/nabo/blob/master/R/WKNNClasses.R)

which produces this in namespace:

export(WKNND)
exportClasses(WKNND)

along with a sensible looking WKNN.Rd file (here 
